@startuml
actor "用户" as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "Spring Boot后端" as Backend
participant "FastAPI AI服务" as AI
database "MySQL" as MySQL
database "向量数据库" as VectorDB
participant "大模型API" as LLM

User -> Frontend : 输入问题
Frontend -> Backend : POST /api/knowledge/ask
Backend -> MySQL : 保存问题记录
Backend -> AI : POST /knowledge/ask
AI -> VectorDB : 相似度检索
VectorDB --> AI : 返回相关文档片段
AI -> LLM : 携带问题和文档片段生成回答
LLM --> AI : 返回回答
AI --> Backend : 答案和引用来源
Backend -> MySQL : 保存答案和引用
Backend --> Frontend : 返回问答结果
Frontend --> User : 展示答案与来源
@enduml
